TenantSecurityCustomMetricStat.name: TenantSecurityCustomMetricStat
TenantSecurityCustomMetricStat.description: Represents custom metric data within Security Center.

ChangeCount.description: The number of times this metric was changed.

CustomMetricIdentifier.description: The ID of the custom metric.

EndProcessTime.description: The end time of the metric being processed.

MetricCount.description: The number of times this metric was recorded.

MetricIdentifier.description: The unique identifier of the metric.

Name.description: The name of the custom metric.

PreviousMetricIdentifier.description: The previous unique identifier of this metric.

StartProcessTime.description: The start time of the metric being processed.

Tenant.description: The ID of the tenant with the custom metric.
